Entities:
---------

** Channel
  * Description:
    - collection of channels

  * Attributes:
    - id
    - label
    - categories
    - country
    - language

  * Associations:
    - has-many categories


** Advert
   * Description:
     - collection of Ads

   * attributes:
     - id
     - label
     - categories
     - country
     - language
     - limit
     - constraint / rule

  * Associations:
    - has-many categories
    - has-one rule

** Category
   * Description:
     - collection of categories
     - tree structure and hence can represent hierarchies

   * Attributes:
     - id
     - label
     - parent
     - children

   * Associations
     - belongs-to Advert

** Country
   * Description:
     - collection of countries

   * Attributes
     - label

** Language
   * Description:
     - collection of languages

   * Attributes
     - label

  * Associations:
    - has-many categories
    - has-one rule


* AdChannelLimit
* AdCountryLimit
